commit.message:
Merge pull request #3 from bitdeli-chef/master

Add a Bitdeli Badge to README
Add a Bitdeli badge to README
BugFix: NextUrl should be set to null when moreResultsAvailable == 0
Bug fix: No need to perform analysis requests when the number of articles is 0
Bug fix: NewsLookupResult.NextUrl should not be set to null if the FilterNewsItemsByPerformanceScore method empties the response from Webhose
X-Next-Url header can now be omitted for initial queries
Bug fix: Added X-Next-Url format checking
Fixed the incorect post-serialization case of NamedEntity
Added political sentiments and named entities in the NLP responses
Improved NLP performance by using batch keyword and analysis APIs
Bug fix: query was not being cleaned up properly for the next URI
Removed Grind.Core/Test + Enabled tests checking Indico texttags bug
Updated WebhoseClient to use pre-existing webhose libraries
